-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Bombardier, GLV Inc, Milestone Apartments 
-- 
-- Fri Sep 26, 2014 06:42AM EDT
-- None



Sept 26 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including GLV Inc and Milestone Apartments REIT, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS* Bombardier <BBDb.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$5.50 from C$5; rating buy * GLV Inc <GLVa.TO>: RBC raises to sector perform from outperform rating * Milestone Apartments REIT <MST_u.TO>: RBC starts with outperform; target price of C$12.50  Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.   * Bombardier <BBDb.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$5.50 from C$5; rating buy * DHX Media Ltd <DHX.TO>: NBF raises target price to C$8.50 from C$8.25; sector perform * Fission Uranium <FCU.V>: Euro Pacific raises target price to $2.20 from $2; rating buy * GLV Inc <GLVa.TO>: Canaccord Genuity cuts target price to C$4.50 from C$5; rating buy * GLV Inc <GLVa.TO>: RBC raises to sector perform from outperform rating * GLV Inc <GLVa.TO>: RBC cuts target price to C$3.50 from C$4 * Horizon North Logistics <HNL.TO>: Raymond James cuts target to C$7 from C$8.50; outperform * Milestone Apartments REIT <MST_u.TO>: RBC starts with outperform; target price of C$12.50 * Stantec <STN.TO>: CIBC raises target price to C$77 from C$75; rating sector outperformer * Vecima Networks <VCM.TO>: CIBC raises price target to C$10 from C$8; sector outperformer